1. Definitions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
:FED.
Electronic payment information
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Electronic delivery of payment information that the customer may
choose to receive via his or her &WEBSYSNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The payment information delivered via the customer's &WEBSYSNAVN.
corresponds to the information stated on a paper-based list of
payments.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
.hy off
.of 4mm
2. Registration to receive electronic payment information
.of
.hy on
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
The customer must observe the "Appendix to the general rules for
Betalingsservice debtors - electronic payment information"
applicable from time to time. If the customer specifically
requests to receive the list of payments in paper form, an
agreement to that effect must be made with &BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Electronic payment information
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
If payments are to be made the following month, the payment
information will be available at the customer's &WEBSYSNAVN. by the end
of the current month. The electronic payment information contains
exactly the same information as the paper-based list of payments. Besides
the list of payments you can receive enclosure with further information
from your creditor.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The customer is responsible for checking the electronic payment
information. If the customer has not received the expected payment
information by the end of the month, the customer must immediately
contact &BANKNAVN so that the payment information may be resent -
either electronically or in paper form.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Rejection of payments, cancellation, etc. of payment agreements
must still take place in accordance with the rules set out in the
"General rules for Betalingsservice debtors". The electronic
payment information may replace an invoice. If the customer needs
to store the payment information for a longer period of time than
offered by &WEBSYSNAVN., the customer may ask &BANKNAVN to explain how
to store or print out the payment information, and what to do if
the customer decides to change banks.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
As a minimum, &WEBSYSNAVN. provides online access to payment
information during the month in which payments are made and the
following 12 months.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
